curse of the faceless man is an independently made 1958 low-budget black-and-white horror film , released by robert e. kent productions and united artists . it was produced by robert e. kent and edward small ( uncredited ) , directed by edward l. cahn , and stars richard anderson and adele mara . the screenplay was written by jerome bixby . the film was theatrically released on a double bill with it ! the terror from beyond space . director cahn also helmed the feature films creature with the atom brain ( 1955 ) , invasion of the saucer men ( 1957 ) and the four skulls of jonathan drake ( 1959 ) .